				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-T%C6%B0-Di%E1%BB%85n/An-Nam-quan-k%E1%BB%B3/poem-cQto19KWG7BGnEFPOQ1lPw">An Nam quan kỳ - 安南觀棋</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-T%C6%B0-Di%E1%BB%85n/author-yjRlicU3gV4B06v3YivzTw">Lý Tư Diễn</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BA%B7ng-Tr%E1%BA%A7n-C%C3%B4n/C%C3%B4-l%C3%A1nh/poem-wwT7Ob_Ote_qRfUA2Yl8zQ">Cô lánh - 孤另</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BA%B7ng-Tr%E1%BA%A7n-C%C3%B4n/author-5S8czaSOqXhHlNE7NtKr8g">Đặng Trần Côn</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/%C4%90%C4%83ng-cao/poem-h3EvqeQvlQUxq2sceUWWYQ">Đăng cao - 登高</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Kh%C3%BAc-giang-tam-ch%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-ch%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-ng%C5%A9-c%C3%BA/poem-pMiSpQReHzAs-F2QhUKUQQ">Khúc giang tam chương, chương ngũ cú - 曲江三章，章五句</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-B%E1%BA%A1ch/K%C3%BD-%C4%90%C3%B4ng-L%E1%BB%97-nh%E1%BB%8B-tr%C4%A9-t%E1%BB%AD/poem-OFHlcAf4xsBFPpF5ew1cWg">Ký Đông Lỗ nhị trĩ tử - 寄東魯二稚子</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-B%E1%BA%A1ch/author-8WYDeeki5xZo8eD-k6Sk5A">Lý Bạch</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-V%C4%A9-Nghi%E1%BB%87p/Th%C3%ADnh-n%E1%BB%AF-%C4%91%E1%BA%A1o-s%C4%A9-Bi%E1%BB%87n-Ng%E1%BB%8Dc-Kinh-%C4%91%C3%A0n-c%E1%BA%A7m-ca/poem-VnEPIiegE3QeuwHP29YN0w">Thính nữ đạo sĩ Biện Ngọc Kinh đàn cầm ca - 聽女道士卞玉京彈琴歌</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-V%C4%A9-Nghi%E1%BB%87p/author-clxY5GFWegDsEw0Y8VPiNQ">Ngô Vĩ Nghiệp</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Ki%E1%BA%BFn/Thu%E1%BB%B7-phu-giao/poem-YNycjtFVEV-cAg2Oi9Zp8A">Thuỷ phu giao - 水夫謠</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Ki%E1%BA%BFn/author-Xw0ALUMVQ06c4vUGFngNbA">Vương Kiến</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Cao-Th%C3%ADch/T%E1%BB%91ng-L%C6%B0u-b%C3%ACnh-s%E1%BB%B1-sung-S%C3%B3c-Ph%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-ph%C3%A1n-quan-ph%C3%BA-%C4%91%E1%BA%AFc-Chinh-m%C3%A3-t%C3%AA/poem-HmzIRodFzLXk1Cs6b3KJHQ">Tống Lưu bình sự sung Sóc Phương phán quan phú đắc “Chinh mã tê” - 送劉評事充朔方判官，賦得征馬嘶</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Cao-Th%C3%ADch/author-daTT9TQ-QJ39piO86WPo5Q">Cao Thích</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Duy%E1%BB%87t/U-Ch%C3%A2u-t%C3%A2n-tu%E1%BA%BF-t%C3%A1c/poem-iYpPD6KWd8X-T-XaF9hWhw">U Châu tân tuế tác - 幽州新歲作</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Duy%E1%BB%87t/author-AKTNQoEgmd-YADK1_8RKQg">Trương Duyệt</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/V%C3%A2n-s%C6%A1n/poem-hocA8plyt2Gb_-d3nA0thQ">Vân sơn - 雲山</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br></div>	</div>
